{"tid":345771,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"﹝成報﹞　港鐵主席　馬時亨　警告　無一地兩檢　市民將無車搭","createTime":"2017-08-03T10:59:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-17T14:50:56.000Z","uid":47714,"like":76,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dfc5250dbecd86398707ee2536ff7b8d69309574","tid":345771,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T10:59:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.singpao.com.hk/index.php?fi=instantnews&amp;id=6978\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.singpao.com.hk%2Findex.php%3Ffi%3Dinstantnews%26id%3D6978&d=9R5E9CeSmXhEJAbl7%2BgU%2FHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=ab259139\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.singpao.com.hk/index.php?fi=instantnews&amp;id=6978</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.singpao.com.hk/image_upload/1501655695.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.singpao.com.hk%2Fimage_upload%2F1501655695.jpg&h=efe822fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港鐵主席馬時亨早上陪同立法會建制派議員到高鐵西九龍總站及石崗列車停放處參觀，民主派議員則杯葛。<br />\n<br />\n馬時亨表示，議員亦看到，工程進度十分良好，一切準備就緒，工程完成95%。馬時亨強調如一地兩檢，在明年立法會休會前不獲通過及未能完成本地立法，市民將會「無車搭」，而西九站用地400萬呎，每月維修費用龐大，重申假如到時不能通車，是「倒錢落海」。 <br />\n<br />\n他表示，高鐵香港段每月營運支出的確實數字目前仍與政府商討中，但強調8000萬元的費用是估算而非預算。營運協議方面，他有信心年底前能與政府完成磋商，解決拆賬及營運問題，冀大眾耐心等候公布。"},{"pid":"1e441d1a75963e054418b4b951093089c7f74459","tid":345771,"uid":19454,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T11:10:48.000Z","msg":"冇得返工，港豬才會驚"},{"pid":"c14cc5c97bcf002cf26308eb2de7625fc263d93e","tid":345771,"uid":23170,"like":66,"dislike":0,"score":66,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T11:10:50.000Z","msg":"無人想搭呀仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0291af9dbe5c92d6c225fb826d3ef9d658fb3c1","tid":345771,"uid":7